data.description: This property has it all! Fully fenced one acre lot with landscaping. Spacious layout with large kitchen for hosting guests! Need to relax? Take a dip in the indoor hot-tub in four seasons room. Need room for the littles? How about an awesome loft with an additional bonus room? There are two large master bedrooms, each with their own bathroom/closets. This property also has a 40x60 3 stall, thermal controlled shop with hydraulic lift, 2 car garage and carport to park your RV and lake toys. Did I mention this has a maintenance free synthetic deck to enjoy the sunsets? Schedule your private showing today!
